# ============================================================================
# WSL Validation Module
# ============================================================================

<#
.SYNOPSIS
    Provides validation functions for WSL installation scripts.

.DESCRIPTION
    This module contains functions for validating usernames, checking
    system availability, and testing WSL distribution status.

